---
title: Seared Monkfish in Pasanda Curry Sauce with Basmati Rice, Mustard Seed Green Beans and Garlic-Coriander Naan
description: Make a meal that's truly special with this lightly indulgent and luxurious Seared Monkfish in Pasanda Curry Sauce.
